equipment carries the data, and provides the behavior that pieces and enemy uses.
(the enemy might reference through pieces)

Here are abstraction categories: 


**Chess-likes: 

    capture(basic) - captures on the square that the piece occupies

    Chess: 
        oct-movement
        cross-movement (rook)
        diagonal-movement (bishop) 
        knight-movement (knight)

        pawn capture - forward two diagonal capture

        more to be added...

    Xiangqi
        cannon capture - 
        more to be added...
    Shogi
        keima capture - forward two knight move
        more to be added...

**In-game unique
    captures: 
        saber - diagonal one space capture 
        sword - horizontal one space capture 
        spear - horizontal two space capture 
